BAGIAN IV — KONTRIBUSI / SECTION IV — CONTRIBUTIONS
================================================================================

Jika Anda ingin berkontribusi pada pengembangan Soraku Community Platform,
Anda harus:

If You wish to contribute to the development of Soraku Community Platform,
You must:

  (a) Menghubungi Soraku Community melalui saluran resmi dan mendapatkan
      persetujuan tertulis sebelum memulai pekerjaan apa pun.

      Contact Soraku Community through official channels and obtain written
      approval before beginning any work.

  (b) Menandatangani Perjanjian Lisensi Kontributor (Contributor License
      Agreement / CLA) yang ditetapkan oleh Soraku Community.

      Sign the Contributor License Agreement (CLA) established by Soraku Community.

  (c) Memahami bahwa setiap kontribusi yang Anda buat secara otomatis menjadi
      milik eksklusif Soraku Community dan tunduk pada lisensi ini.

      Understand that any contribution You make automatically becomes the
      exclusive property of Soraku Community and is subject to this license.

